Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL STORY BY NATSU HYUUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICION, AND ALL NAMES OF FIGURES ND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}MOREOVER, THE STORY HAS NO RELATION TO REAL-LIFE INCIDENTS AND EVENTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair's so sticky…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not young,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I'd like him to stop working at the farm…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But he sure loves making medicine out of herbs he grew himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know you. Are you an outside apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-The old man… -Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the apothecary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Quickly! {\i1}-This smell…!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Apothecary! I made them vomit it out, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her breath is weak too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check whether there's any vomit in his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-You check her. -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has no pulse. Nothing in his throat, either.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just saliva.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make them drink water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Charcoal. Bring some charcoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this, so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take a bath…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ms. Apothecary. They're both stable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, leave that. -Even the vomit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-There might be poison left over. -Poison…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sick people were a courtesan and her customer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The room was filled with the scent of alcohol and tobacco.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two liquor bottles.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shattered glass cups.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this… wheat stalk?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A smoking pipe, and tobacco leaves.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What an elaborate act this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some charcoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you bring a wood tablet and something to write with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man should be at the farm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by the southern outer walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you bring him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl was concerned for my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I crushed the charcoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll mix it with the herbs and have them take it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you drink this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's okay. He took the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess your treatment was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just "all right"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old man is someone who can learn two or three things{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}out of a single piece of information.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What poison did you think this was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here it comes!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old man tries to teach me lessons like this sometimes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobacco leaves are poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what they'd use for a suicide pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you didn't make them drink water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That would have reverse effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastric fluid can prevent the absorption of poison,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so in that case, water wouldn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if this was dissolved in water in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are no leaves in the vomit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I missed it. Am I still half-asleep?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the poison was dissolved in water, it's better to dilute it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right. Now I know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offering tea sweets reserved for guests?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're quite generous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They use this to prevent lipstick stains on the cups.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped us a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mere token, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, I can't accept that… -Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you afford rent to Grams this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I happily accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez. This old man…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This instance was{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a classic case of a suicide pact. Not uncommon here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A woman with a long term of service{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a man that can't afford to buy her out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Couples like that always have one plan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that man… He was dressed in expensive clothing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has a handsome face.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't seem to have a problem with money or women.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though I'm making assumptions. Old man wouldn't like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't seem the type to take poison for his future with a courtesan…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man's condition was more serious.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way! Bastards like him should die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Apothecary, can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a very problematic customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He would say sweet words to courtesans,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}act as if he were buying them out,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then abandon them once he got bored.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He incurred a lot of wrath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'd almost get stabbed by an enraged woman,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or get poisoned.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's spoiled by his father, who's a wealthy merchant.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every time, he would resolve problems with money.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he would come to brothels accompanied by guards that he asked his parents for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Her older sister was also abandoned by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She was looking forward to living with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but he took it back on the day of the buyout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she couldn't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She was attached to the courtesan that drank the poison today, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm supposed to pretend I didn't see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Customers like that shouldn't be permitted to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her that fell for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it led to today's suicide pact incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely a bad look for the brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They must've been so generous with us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because we prevented the death of a wealthy merchant's son at their business.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's why…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This situation must've felt so unjust to this girl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just happened to be back home today.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if she runs errands every day,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she might have known the hours that old man is out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally, one would call a doctor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she purposefully came to call on an absent apothecary…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That apprentice girl… She's small, but frightening.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a situation for you, after you came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man. Show me the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup. There's money inside.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Along with an added amount of hush money.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But something about this bothers me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From what I hear, the man doesn't seem the delicate type.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would a man like that make a suicide pact for a woman he loves?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a forced suicide pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But would a man who had been poisoned before be so careless…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao. I told you, don't make assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know the truth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me remember.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was at the scene?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I miss anything?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tobacco leaves are poisonous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what they'd use for a suicide pact.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what if this was dissolved in water in the first place?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her that fell for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bastards like him should die!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was attached to the courtesan that drank the poison today, so…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. They use this to prevent lipstick stains on the cups.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't a suicide pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Substance dissolved in water… Wheat stalk…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different types of alcohol…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A murder, not a suicide pact.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the murderer was the courtesan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The murder weapon was alcohol poisoned with tobacco.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how did she make the man drink the poison, when he was so cautious{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of his safety that he had personal guards?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quite simple.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could drink it herself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the courtesan is safe, the man would drink the alcohol, too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if she actually drank the poisonous alcohol, she'd be in danger.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why she used those tools.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two types of alcohol and one cup.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Different types of alcohol differ in richness and density.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you pour light alcohol slowly on top of heavy alcohol,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will create aesthetically pleasing layers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she performed this trick as a way to please customers,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the courtesan could drink only the bottom layer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}using the wheat stalk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The courtesan also drank the top layer alcohol.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only a small amount, so that she wouldn't die.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The plan would be pointless if she died as well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She calculated the timing{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that he would die, and she would survive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why it happened in the morning.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And conveniently, someone found them like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is delicate,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but tough at the same time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stay asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The apprentice's actions were a bit off.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She went to the apothecary{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and not the doctor so that the man would run out of time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She took her time to bring old man.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was she not concerned for her "Big Sis"?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she not think that just like her{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}actual older sister, someone close to her could die again?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost as if she knew she wouldn't die.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could be. Or I'm just overthinking things.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the courtesan who was oddly sympathetic to the apprentice.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The granny who paid us well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone can seem suspicious if you view them that way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that everyone was…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't be making assumptions.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to come back here for a long time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But here's no different than the rear palace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a flower garden, a bird cage.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All become poisoned by the air in this trapped environment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the courtesans, by eating others' poisons,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}themselves become sweet poison.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,THE VERDIGRIS HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what will happen to that courtesan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spoiled son could{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}claim and complain that he got poisoned,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or it could be that{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the brothel threatens him for ruining their merchandise.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we troubled our minds about these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd never survive this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Meimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already going back to the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a year left in my term of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I quit my job, I'd cause trouble to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But you only just got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was so worried after you went missing suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pairin, Juka, and Granny too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But they didn't mention that at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone acted like nothing was wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that make you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Big Sis Meimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao. Did you go to the annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My three-day homecoming{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ended before I realized.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already going home? What a disappointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Sir Lihaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! What a disappointment, truly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like he enjoyed his time here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once you taste the sweet nectar of the heavens,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you can't come back to earth.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll continue to get squeezed out so that he neither lives nor dies.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one paying for what the advance payment couldn't cover.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me when you're back, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I know exactly where I'm selling myself to next.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is he glaring at me like that?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get out of here quickly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go change now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tell us… -Everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you in the reception room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His attitude is worse than usual.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I just imagining things?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope that's the case. We'll put it that way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But… why is it just the two of us?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you visited home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone seemed to be doing well. I was glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what kind of man is this Lihaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my surety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does he know his name?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He has to be of a certain status.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, he can't be my surety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he give you a hair clip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was handing several of them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an obligatory gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to tell me I lost to an obligatory gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you one also.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I"? What?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he's in a bad mood because I didn't propose an offer to him?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's very strange.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's better not to get involved in troublesome things.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's always bored.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he want attention, even when it's troublesome?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not think of a worthy payment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that would satisfy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make this "payment" to this Lihaku man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. He seemed happy with his one night of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed extremely satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I worked hard too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this, before it stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You should wash this right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry this teacup away, so don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW OF NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Next episode, "Suicide or Murder?"{\i}
